ddbf89","tid":25844,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ac1acb5a2ee91c297c1fb31b047dd0acd2e4829","tid":25844,"uid":3523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e55b997197d47a33b324636f373d3f4fa4aed27","tid":25844,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:37:37.000Z","msg":"講下就算 咪同你一樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係得把口拎光環 無撚用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"一個連登會員9成膠post 可以睇得出香港前景<br />\n<br />\n咁清高嘅post大家點可以唔討論？唔討論香港前景走去討論娛樂新聞就係鬼！<br />\n<br />\n一個明星出軌 可以睇得出香港前景（入嚟睇一眼都好）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1109165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1109165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n但清高post點解又要開膠post?唔通清高巴打要學共狗限制連登會員討論嘅話題？<br />\n<br />\n好想同男朋友做 但佢係基督徒.....堅持婚後性行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1105061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1105061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n條女同我講有咗bb但其實我有不育症 你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1105575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1105575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n我係一個混血兒 由細到大都成日俾人蝦俾人笑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1092968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1092968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一時又男朋友又女朋友咁點算清高呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（有圖）俾唔鍾意嘅女仔纏 尋晚仲要send啲咁嘅相嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1080761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1080761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n男朋友第二次出軌 放過佢放過我自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1059537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1059537</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n出軌post自己有份開 唔比熱門post討論許志安黃心穎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開唔開post好？"},{"pid":"fcf21d6dafa176aa43c713a1d66b1325d01b5edb","tid":25844,"uid":3523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T